quran[182]{c,v,t}:
  37,1,"Ndarahiye Jewe Allah, ku bamalayika batonda ku murongo mu gusenga;"
  37,2,"No ku bamalayika basunika ibicu vy’imvura kw’itegeko ryanje;"
  37,3,"No ku bamalayika basoma urwibutso n’amajambo yanje mu guhishurira Intumwa!"
  37,4,"Mu vy’ukuri ga bantu! Imana yanyu mukwiye gusenga Itabangikanywa, ni Imana Imwe Rudende Allah."
  37,5,"Ni Yo Mana Rurema Yaremye amajuru n’isi n’ibiri hagati yavyo, ni na Yo Mubungabunzi w’izuba mu buseruko no mu burengero bwaryo."
  37,6,"Mu vy’ukuri Twebwe Allah, Twarasharije n’inyenyeri ijuru ryegereye isi;"
  37,7,"Turaheza Turaribungabunga, kugira ntirivogerwe n’uwo wese mu ntagondwa z’amashetani;"
  37,8,"Amashetani rero, ntashobora gushika ahari abamalayika mu majuru ngo aheze asume urusaku kw’ihishurwa ry’ibijanye n’amabwirizwa, ivyagezwe hamwe n’ishirwa mu ngiro ryavyo. Amashetani ahirahiye agasuma urusaku, aca aterwa ibishirira vya nyakotsi biturutse ku mpande zose;"
  37,9,"Akirukanwa kugira ntashobore gusuma nya rusaku, yaranategekanirijwe n’ibihano vyamaho mu buzima bw’inyuma yo gupfa;"
  37,10,"Kiretse shetani isamiye hejuru ijambo rimwe muri iryo suma ry’urusaku, igaca iribwira iyiri musi yayo; ino na yo ikaribwira iyindi iri musi yayo gushika ku yiri kw’isi. Hari n’aho rero, ikurikizwa igishirira ca nyakotsi kikayiturira imbere yuko iribwira iyiri musi yayo. Hari n’igihe bishika rero mu vyagezwe n’Imana Allah, ikarisamira hejuru ikaribwira iyiri musi yayo imbere yuko ishikirwa na nya gishirira kikayiturira, maze iya nyuma muri yo ikarishikiriza ba senyagara n’abapfumu, na bo bagaca baryuhirako ayandi majambo ijana y’ikinyoma."
  37,11,"Ntumwa y’Imana! Baza abahakana bivuye inyuma izurwa ry’ibiremwa, ko iremwa ryabo ari ryo rigoye cane gusumba iremwa ry’ibindi biremwa Twaremye! Mu vy’ukuri Twebwe Allah, Twaremye se wabo Adamu mw’ivu ribomvye."
  37,12,"Ntumwa y’Imana! Ahubwo icogutangaza, ni ihakana ryabo ry’izurwa ry’ibiremwa; n’icogutangaza kurusha, ni itebura ryabo kuri wewe n’isuzugurwa ry’amajambo yawe!"
  37,13,"N’iyo bibukijwe ku vyo bibagiye canke bakagotwa, ukubibutsa nta co kubamarira ngo bikebuke."
  37,14,"N’iyo babonye icemezo cerekana ko uri Intumwa vy’ukuri, baragiteburako bakitangaza;"
  37,15,"Bagaheza bakavuga bati: “Iyi Qor’ani watuzaniye, si ikindi kiretse ko ari uburozi bweruye;"
  37,16,"Mbega igihe twapfuye tugacika ivu n’amagufa yaboze, burya mu vy’ukuri tuzosubizwa ubuzima duheze tuzuke!"
  37,17,"Mbega burya hazozuka na ba data bapfuye kera!”"
  37,18,"Ntumwa y’Imana! Vuga ubwire abahakana bivuye inyuma izurwa ry’ibiremwa uti: “Ego cane! Bitebe bitebuke, muzosubizwa ubuzima maze muzuke kandi musuzuguritse”."
  37,19,"Ni ukuri, izurwa ryabo ni akaravyo, hazopfa kuvuzwa inzamba igira kabiri gusa, ubwo nyene bace basokoroka mu kuzimu birabira intureka zo ku musi w’izuka;"
  37,20,"Baheze bavuge n’agahinda n’akantu bati: “Amagorwa arama yemwe! Uwu, ni wo musi w’iharurirwa n’impera!”;"
  37,21,"Bace babwirwa n’abamalayika bati: “Uwu, ni wo musi wo gutunganiriza ibiremwa, umusi mwahora muhakana mwivuye inyuma mukiri kw’isi ko utabaho”."
  37,22,"Abamalayika bazobwirwa bati: “Nimwegeranirize hamwe abirenganije mu kugarariza bari kumwe n’abagenzi babo, hamwe rero n’ibigirwamana bahora basenga;"
  37,23,"Bakabisenga mu gishingo c’Imana Allah, muheze mubashorere mu nzira ibashikana mu muriro ururumba;"
  37,24,"Maze mubahagarike aho babanza kubazwa imbere yuko batabwa mu muriro wa Jahannamu; mu vy’ukuri, bategerezwa kubazwa ku vyo bakoze no ku vyo bavuze vyose”."
  37,25,"Bazoheza rero babwirwe ku gashinyaguro n’akantu bati: “Mbega mwafashwe n’iki ko mudatabarana nk’uko mwabigenza kw’isi!”."
  37,26,"Ahubwo kuri uwu musi, bicishije bugufi mu kwubahiriza itegeko ry’Imana Allah, ntibashobora namba guca kubiri na ryo."
  37,27,"Aho rero, bazoheza batangure guhazana, bahangane hagati yabo batanako imiragwe;"
  37,28,"Maze indongozi z’abahuvye zibwirwe n’abazikurikiye mu buhuvyi ziti: “Mu vy’ukuri, ni mwebwe mwahora mutuja mu gutwi mukatwankisha ukuri, mukaturyohereza ubuhuvyi kw’izina ry’idini”."
  37,29,"Indongozi z’abahuvye na zo zibwire abazikurikiye mu buhuvyi ziti: “Sigaho, murabaga mwifashe! Ahubwo nyabuna, mwebwe ntimwigeze mwemera namba;"
  37,30,"Vyongeye nta n’ububasha bw’ivyemezo canke bw’inguvu twari tubafiseko ngo tubabuze ukwemera Imana Allah, eka mbere mwari mwigize akagaramaruganda mu guhonyanga ukuri mukubona;"
  37,31,"Ni ho rero twebwe hamwe na mwe twagirwa n’ijambo ry’Imana yacu Rurema Allah, ryo gusezeranira ibihano abagarariji. Mu vy’ukuri rero, twese hamwe dutegerezwa guhonja ibihano;"
  37,32,"Twebwe twarabahubishije inzira y’ukwemera, muraheza muradukurikira mu buhuvyi, mu vy’ukuri twari twarahuvye”."
  37,33,"Mu vy’ukuri kuri uwo musi rero, indongozi z’abahuvye hamwe n’abazikurikiye mu buhuvyi, bazofadikanya mu bihano nk’uko bafadikanije kw’isi mu buhuvyi."
  37,34,"Ni nk’ukwo nyene rero Twebwe Allah, Tugira mu guhana inkozi z’ikibi zahisemwo ubugaba kw’isi ha kutwumvira."
  37,35,"Mu vy’ukuri, ababangikanyamana bakiri kw’isi, iyo bararikiwe gusenga Imana Imwe Rudende Allah, bati: “Nta mana ibwirijwe gusengwa atari Imana Allah”, bahora bagira amanyama bakirengagiza;"
  37,36,"Bagaca bavuga bati: “Mbega vyoshoboka gute mu vy’ukuri, ko tureka gusenga imana zacu ku kwubahiriza gusa ijambo ry’umwivuzi w’amazina, yakehewe n’ubwenge!”."
  37,37,"Nibateshwe bate barahumba! Muhamadi ntari nk’ukwo bamuvuga namba, ahubwo yaje abazaniye ukuri kw’ukwemera gushingiye kuri Qor’ani, ashimangira ivyashikirijwe n’izindi Ntumwa mu mabwirizwa n’isengwa ry’Imana Imwe Rudende Allah."
  37,38,"Babangikanyamana! Mu vy’ukuri, mwebwe ku kubera ihakana ryanyu, mutegerezwa guhonja ibihano bibabaza;"
  37,39,"Kandi mu buzima bw’inyuma yo gupfa, ntimuzohanwa, kiretse ku vyaha mwari mwarakoze kw’isi."
  37,40,"Kiretse abaja b’Imana Allah bayitumbera mu vyo bakora vyose bakabikora ku bwayo, maze Igaheza Ikabakingira ibihano;"
  37,41,"Abo, ni bo rero bazoronka impano zizwi neza kandi zamaho mu Bwami bw’ijuru;"
  37,42,"Izo mpembo, ni ivyamwa vy’ubwoko butandukanye, bakazonaterwa iteka n’icubahiro;"
  37,43,"Mu Bwami bw’ijuru bwuzuyemwo inema zamaho;"
  37,44,"Aho bazoba bicaye ku bitanda batumberanye, barabana;"
  37,45,"Ibirahuri vy’inzoga itambiye bicanacanako, inzoga yengwa mu mazi y’iriba ritemba ryamaho;"
  37,46,"Ifise ibara ryera n'akanovera k’akataraboneka ku banywi bazoyihereza;"
  37,47,"Ntigira ingaruka mbi ngo iboreze canke ngo isinzikaze ubuzima bw’uwuguma ayinywa;"
  37,48,"Muri nya Bwami, bazoba bafise n’abakenyezi biyubashe bisoneye, batigera bakubita ijisho abatari abagabo babo, bafise n’amaso meza nk’ay’inyana;"
  37,49,"Basa neza, ntiworaba barasayangana; wogira ngo ni irigi ribitswe ahantu ata n’umwe ararikorako."
  37,50,"Abari mu Bwami bw’ijuru, bazobazanya hagati yabo, batera inkuru z’ubuzima babanyemwo n’abandi kw’isi;"
  37,51,"Maze umwe muri bo aheze avuge ati: “Mu vy’ukuri, kw’isi nari mfise umugenzi twamana hafi;"
  37,52,"Yavuga yitangaza ambwira ati: “Mbega mu vy’ukuri, wewe uri mu bemera ko izurwa ry’ibiremwa ribaho!"
  37,53,"Aho nyene uremera ko nitwapfa tugacika ivu n’amagufa mu kuzimu, tuzoheza tugasubizwa ubuzima tukazuka koko, hanyuma tugaharurirwa, tukanahemberwa ivyo twakoze!””."
  37,54,"Hanyuma wa mwemeramana, ace avuga abwire abo bari kumwe mu Bwami bw’ijuru, ati: “Ubwo ntimwoza tukarunguruka mu muriro tukaraba iherezo ry’uwahoze ari umugenzi twamana hafi!”;"
  37,55,"Wa mwemeramana agize ngo ararunguruka mu muriro, aca abona wa mugenzi wiwe bamana hafi, ari hagati na hagati mu nyenga y’umuriro ururumba;"
  37,56,"Aca avuga abwira nya mugenzi wiwe ati: “Ndarahiye kw’izina ry’Imana Allah, ko wahatswe kumpubisha ngahona iyo ndakwumvira;"
  37,57,"Iyo hataba impano y’Imana yanje Rurema Allah, Yanshoboje kwemera nkatsimbatara, ni ukuri nari kuba ndi mu begeranirijwe hamwe na we mu muriro”."
  37,58,"Ba bemeramana aho bari mu Bwami bw’ijuru, baca bavuga akamwemwe kabasya bati: “Ni ivy’ukuri, ko tuzoguma mu nema zamaho ibihe bidahera ata gupfa;"
  37,59,"Kiretse urupfu rwa mbere twapfuye tukiri kw’isi, nta n’uguhanwa inyuma y’aho twinjiriye mu Bwami bw’ijuru!"
  37,60,"Mu vy’ukuri, iyi ni yo ntsinzi ihambaye”."
  37,61,"Mu ntumbero yo gushika ku ntsinzi nk’iyi y’Ubwami bw’ijuru, abakora ivyo bakora kw’isi rero, nibakore batiziganya, ata kudebukirwa."
  37,62,"Mbega none burya iyo ntsinzi y’Ubwami bw’ijuru, ni ryo cumbi ryiza cane kuruta ibindi, canke ni igiti Al-Zaqquumu cavumwe, gifungurirwa abantu bo mu muriro!"
  37,63,"Mu vy’ukuri Twebwe Allah, Twagize ico giti kuba igeragezwa ku birenganije mu kugarariza, bahakana bivuye inyuma bati: “Bishoboka gute ko igiti kiba mu muriro kandi umuriro uturira igiti!”."
  37,64,"Al-Zaqquumu mu vy’ukuri, ni igiti kinagira hagati na hagati mu nyenga y’umuriro wa Jahannamu;"
  37,65,"Ivyamwa vya nya giti bisa nabi cane; wogira ngo ni imitwe y’amashetani, ntubaze rero akanuko kavyo n’ukuntu bibishe (bikata) mu kanwa!"
  37,66,"Mu vy’ukuri ababangikanyamana, bazorya ivyamwa vyaco, bibuzuze inda batumbirwe;"
  37,67,"Hanyuma bashozeko ikinyobwa kigizwe n’uruvange rw’amashira n’urwuya vy’abantu bo mu muriro vyasebuye bikaryimara;"
  37,68,"Hanyuma iyegeranirizo ryabo inyuma y’ivyo vyose, ni mu bihano vyo mu muriro."
  37,69,"Mu vy’ukuri ababangikanyamana, basanze ba se babo ari impuvyi mw’ibangikanyamana;"
  37,70,"Baraheza bacanacanako mu kubakurikira mu buhuvyi."
  37,71,"Ntumwa y’Imana! Ni ukuri mu bantu bo hambere y’abo warungitsweko, harimwo benshi bahuvye;"
  37,72,"Ni ukuri, Twarabarungikiye Intumwa zibagabisha ku bihano vyacu, maze ntibumva, baragarariza."
  37,73,"Ntumwa y’Imana! Raba rero iherezo ry’abantu bagabishijwe maze ntibumva, ukuntu ryagenze, barahanwe bimwe vy’akarorero;"
  37,74,"Kiretse abaja b’Imana Allah bayitumbera mu vyo bakora vyose, maze bakabikora ku bwayo, Igaheza Ikabakingira ibihano."
  37,75,"Ni ukuri, Nuhu amaze kwihebura ko abantu yarungitsweko batarota bamwemera, yaraduhamagaye Twebwe Allah kugira Tumutabare, maze asanga ni Twebwe Umwiza w’abatabazi yitabira uwumutabaje;"
  37,76,"Turaheza rero Turamurokora we n’umuryango wiwe hamwe n’abemeramana bari kumwe, Tubakura mu kaga ko gusomeshwa nturi y’akataraboneka;"
  37,77,"Maze Tugira uruvyaro rwa Nuhu kuba ari rwo rusigara rukarondoka inyuma yuko abantu yarungitsweko bahitanwa n’isegenya;"
  37,78,"Tumuha no kuyagwa neza mu bantu bakurikiye gushika ku musi w’iherezo."
  37,79,"Harakayagwa neza rero Nuhu mw’iteka n’itekane mu biremwa vyose."
  37,80,"Ni nk’uko nyene rero mu vy’ukuri Twebwe Allah - Twahemvye Nuhu mu kuyagwa neza n’ibiremwa - Duhemba abagwaneza mu kwumvira Imana Allah."
  37,81,"Mu vy’ukuri, Nuhu ari mu baja bacu b’abemeramana bubahiriza koko amabwirizwa yacu."
  37,82,"Mu nyuma rero, ni ho Twebwe Allah, Twahonya abantu ba Nuhu bahakanye bivuye inyuma, maze bahitanwa n’isegenya."
  37,83,"Mu vy’ukuri, mu bagendeye ukwemera-ndemanwa kwa Nuhu gushingiye ku kwemera no gusenga Imana Imwe Rudende Allah, ni Umuvugishwamana Ibrahimu;"
  37,84,"Igihe yatumbera Imana yiwe Rurema Allah n’umutima wejejwe mu kutemera ibintazi n’ingeso mbi;"
  37,85,"Igihe abwira se wiwe n’abantu yarungitsweko ati: “Ni ibiki musenga mu gishingo c’Imana Allah!"
  37,86,"Karashize ingani, mukanagare mwihe gusenga imana z’irementanya ha gusenga Imana Imwe Rudende Allah!"
  37,87,"Mbega none mwibaza iki ku co Imana Rurema w’ibiremwa vyose Yobahanisha mu gihe mwoyibangikanya!”."
  37,88,"Ni ho rero Ibrahimu yitegereza inyenyeri yiyumvira ico yobigobotoza mu kutajana na bo ku musi mukuru wabo;"
  37,89,"Aca ababwira ati: “Mu vy’ukuri jewe ndarwaye”."
  37,90,"Baraheza rero baramureka arasigara, na bo barabandanya ku musi mukuru wabo."
  37,91,"Ni ho rero yagenda anyaragasa ahari ibigirwamana vyabo, aca abibwira atebura abinebagura ati: “Aho ga ntu, ntimwofungura kuri izi mfungurwa muterekerwa n’ababasenga!"
  37,92,"Mbega mwafashwe n’iki ko mutavuga, ngo mwishure n’uwubabajije!”."
  37,93,"Ni ho rero yarengera kuri nya bigirwamana, arabikubita n’ukuryo arabimenagura."
  37,94,"Ba bantu ni ho baja kumurondera baza batazambaye n’ishavu n’akantu;"
  37,95,"Ibrahimu araheza ahura na bo ababwira ata co yinona ati: “Bishoboka gute ko musenga ivyo mwibaziye mwebwe nyene;"
  37,96,"Mugaheza mukareka kwiyegereza Imana Allah mu vyo mukora ntimunayisenge, kandi ari Yo Yabaremye, Ikarema n’ivyo mukora!”."
  37,97,"Ba bantu bamaze kwumva ko ata kuri bafise ngo biregure, baciye babicisha mu ngimba babwirana hagati yabo bati: “Nimumwubakireko, maze mugire inkonge y'umuriro, muheze mumuteyo”."
  37,98,"Bagomvye rero kumugirira nabi ngo bamwice, Turaheza Twebwe Allah, Turabatsinda mu gutegeka nya muriro ko utohirahira ngo umukoreko."
  37,99,"Ibrahimu yababwiye ati: “Jewe mu vy’ukuri, ndimukiye aho nshobora kwiyegereza Imana yanje Rurema mu vyo nkora vyose ndanayisenga mu mwidegemvyo, Izoheza Inshikane ku vyiza mw’idini no mu buzima bwanje bwo kw’isi”;"
  37,100,"Araheza yitura Imana Allah ayisaba avuga ati: “Mana yanje Rurema Allah! Ndagusavye Umpe umwana mu beranda”;"
  37,101,"Twaramwumviye igisabisho ciwe, Turaheza Tumuha agakuru keza ko azoronswa umwana w’umuhungu azorangwa n’ubwitonzi nta ngere."
  37,102,"Ismayili rero amaze gukura akagera mu bigero vyo kujana na Ibrahimu mu dukorwa twa misi yose, Ibrahimu yamubwiye ati: “Mwananje! Ni ukuri, jewe narose mbona vy’ukuri ndiko ndagukerera, none ubivuzeko iki?”. Ismayili yishuye se ata gushidikanya ati: “Da! Shira mu ngiro ivyo wategetswe n’Imana Allah, maze unkerere, nanje uza gusanga ku bushake bw’Imana Allah ndi mu bihangana mu kwumvira Imana Allah”."
  37,103,"Bompi rero bamaze kwitegurira kwubahiriza iryo tegeko, maze Ibrahimu akarambika Ismayili hasi yubitse inda kugira amukerere;"
  37,104,"Ni ho Twahamagara Ibrahimu muri ivyo bihe bigoye Duti: “Ewe Ibrahimu!"
  37,105,"Ni ukuri, wamaze gushira mu ngiro ico wategetswe mu ndoto. Ni nk’uko nyene rero mu vy’ukuri Twebwe Allah - Twahemvye Ibrahimu kw’ishirwa mu ngiro ry’indoto yiwe - Duhemba abagwaneza mu kubakura mu vyago mu buzima bwo kw’isi no mu bw’inyuma yo gupfa;"
  37,106,"Mu vy’ukuri ikererwa ry’umwana wawe Ismayili, ni ryo geragezwa rihambaye ryerekana ukuri kw’ukwemera kwawe”."
  37,107,"Ni ukwo rero Twarokoye Ismayili, haraheza hakererwa imbagwa y’intama mu kibanza ciwe."
  37,108,"Gutyo Duha Ibrahimu kuyagwa neza mu bantu bakurikiye gushika ku musi w’iherezo."
  37,109,"Ibrahimu arakagira amahoro, iteka n’itekane bivuye ku Mana Allah."
  37,110,"Ni nk’uko nyene rero Twebwe Allah - Twahemvye Ibrahimu ku kwubahiriza ibwirizwa ryacu - Duhemba abagwaneza."
  37,111,"Mu vy’ukuri, Ibrahimu ari mu baja bacu b’abemeramana koko."
  37,112,"Ibrahimu mu kumuhembera ukwihangana kw’ishirwa mu ngiro ry’ibwirizwa ryacu, Twaranamuhaye agakuru keza ko kuzoronswa umwana yitwa Is-haka, akazoba n’Umuvugishwamana mu Bavugishwamana beranda;"
  37,113,"Maze Turamuhezagira we hamwe n’umwana wiwe Is-haka. Mu ruvyaro rwabo bompi rero, hahavuye habonekamwo umwumviramana w’umugwaneza koko, hamwe rero n’uwirenganya bimwe biboneka mu kugarariza."
  37,114,"Ni ukuri Musa na murumunawe Haruna, Twarabateye iteka ryo kuba Intumwa;"
  37,115,"Turaheza Turabarokora bompi hamwe n’abantu babo mu vyago bihambaye vyo gusoma nturi;"
  37,116,"Maze Turabatabara, baranesha Firawuni hamwe n’abunganizi biwe;"
  37,117,"Twaranabahaye Igitabu ca Tawurati gitomoye;"
  37,118,"Tubarongora no mu nzira igororotse y’ubwislamu;"
  37,119,"Gutyo, Tubaha kuyagwa neza mu bantu bakurikiye gushika ku musi w’iherezo."
  37,120,"Musa na murumunawe Haruna barakagira amahoro, iteka n’itekane bivuye ku Mana Allah."
  37,121,"Ni nk’uko nyene rero Twebwe Allah - Twahemvye Musa na Haruna - Duhemba abagwaneza b’imvugakuri."
  37,122,"Mu vy’ukuri Musa na murumunawe Haruna, bari mu baja bacu b’abemeramana koko."
  37,123,"Mu vy’ukuri Ilyaasi, ni ukuri ari mu bo Twateye iteka ryo kuba Intumwa;"
  37,124,"Igihe yabwira abantu biwe yarungitsweko muri Bene Israyeli ati: “Nimutinye ibihano vy’Imana Allah, ntimuhirahire ngo muyibangikanye;"
  37,125,"Bishoboka gute ko musenga ikigirwamana ata na kimwe gishoboye, mukirengagiza gusenga Umwiza w’abaremyi;"
  37,126,"Imana yanyu Rurema Allah Yabaremye, Ikaba ari na Yo Mana Yaremye ba so aho hambere yanyu!”."
  37,127,"Abantu Ilyaasi yarungitsweko rero, baramuhakanye bivuye inyuma. Mu vy’ukuri ku musi w’izuka, bazokwegeranirizwa ku Mana Allah kugira Ibahanire ivyo bakoze;"
  37,128,"Kiretse abaja b’Imana Allah bejeje idini ryayo, abo ntibazohanwa."
  37,129,"Ilyaasi Twamuhaye kuyagwa neza mu bantu bakurikiye gushika ku musi w’iherezo."
  37,130,"Ilyaasi arakagira amahoro, iteka n’itekane bivuye ku Mana Allah."
  37,131,"Mu vy’ukuri, ni nk’uko nyene rero Twebwe Allah - Twahemvye Ilyaasi kw’igamburukiramana ryiwe - Duhemba abagwaneza mu bemeramana."
  37,132,"Mu vy’ukuri Ilyaasi, ari mu baja bacu bubahiriza koko amabwirizwa yacu."
  37,133,"Mu vy’ukuri Luutwi, ni ukuri ari mu bo Twateye iteka ryo kuba Intumwa;"
  37,134,"Igihe Twamurokora we hamwe n’umuryango wiwe mu bihano;"
  37,135,"Kiretse umukecuru ari aho, yahonejwe mu bandi ku bubegito bwiwe."
  37,136,"Mu nyuma rero, ni ho Twahonya vy’akarorero abahakanyi mu bantu ba Luutwi."
  37,137,"Bantu b’i Makka! Mu vy’ukuri mu ruja n’uruza rwanyu, ni ukuri mwama muzinduka muca ahahoze imihana y’abantu ba Luutwi;"
  37,138,"Mukanagorobeza muhaca. Ubwo ntimwogarura akenge mugatinya ko mwoshikirwa n’ivyabashikiye."
  37,139,"Mu vy’ukuri Yunusu, ni ukuri ari mu bo Twateye iteka ryo kuba Intumwa;"
  37,140,"Igihe atwarwa n’agashavu agata abantu biwe yarungitsweko, agahungira mu bwato bwuzuye abantu n’ibintu;"
  37,141,"Maze nya bwato bukubitwa n’imikuba iturutse irya n’ino, biba ngombwa ko baburemururira kugira ntibwibire. Ni ho rero bagira tombora ku kuraba uwotabwa mw’ibahari, maze amajwi yose agwa kuri Yunusu;"
  37,142,"Araheza atabwa mw’ibahari, ifi amahanga iba yamubonye nk’ejo ica iramusama, iramutamira ku mwikomo yari afitiwe n’Imana Allah."
  37,143,"Iyo Yunusu rero ataba ari mu bantu barangwa no gukora ivyiza imbere yuko atamirwa na nya fi, hanyuma akaguma aninahaza yongera atazira Imana Allah ari mu nda yayo;"
  37,144,"Ni ukuri yari gupfira mu nda yayo, maze akagumayo gushika ku musi w’izurwa ry’ibiremwa."
  37,145,"Ni ho rero Twamukura muri nya fi Tukamuterera kw’isi y’ubugaragwa, yarushe yacitse intere;"
  37,146,"Turaheza Tumunagishiriza igiti c’uruyuzi kimuha agatutu, akanagifungurako gushika atore mitende."
  37,147,"Mu nyuma, Twahavuye Tumurungika ku bantu ibihumbi ijana, mbere n’abarenga;"
  37,148,"Maze baramwemera baranashira mu ngiro ivyo abigisha, Duca Tubaha kuryoherwa n’ubuzima bwo kw’isi gushika kw’isango ryo gupfa kwabo."
  37,149,"Ntumwa y’Imana! Baza abantu warungitsweko ukuntu bubahuka bakomekera abakobwa ku Mana yawe Rurema Allah ku rwanko gusa babafitiye, maze bakigenera abahungu ku rukundo babafitiye!"
  37,150,"Babaze kandi bakwereke ko ariho bari bari, igihe Twebwe Allah Turema abamalayika ari abakobwa nk’uko babivuga!"
  37,151,"Emwe bantu! Nimwumve mwumvireho! Ni ukuri mu binyoma vy’ababangikanyamana, bavuga ko;"
  37,152,"Imana Allah Yavyaye. Mu vy’ukuri, barabesha bagaheba bakanyomoza ku kuvuga ivyo batazi."
  37,153,"Imana Allah Yokwihitiramwo gute abakobwa Ikirengagiza abahungu!"
  37,154,"Bantu! Iyo, ni ingingo mbi cane mwishingira, ko Imana Allah Yigeneye abakobwa mu biremwa, na mwe Ikabagenera abahungu!"
  37,155,"Ubwo ntimwokwibuka mukamenya ko bitabereye namba ko Imana Allah Yitirirwa umwana! Ntibikabe."
  37,156,"Canke mwoba mufise ku vyo muvuga, icemezo gitomoye gishingiye ku bumenyi!"
  37,157,"Nimwaba rero mufise nya cemezo kiri mu Gitabu c’Imana Allah, enda nyabuna rero, nimukizane nimwaba muri imvugakuri koko!"
  37,158,"Ababangikanyamana bibwira ko Imana Allah hari ico Ipfana n’abamalayika gishingiye ku maraso. Ni ukuri abamalayika, barazi neza ko ababangikanyamana bazokwegeranirizwa mu bihano ku musi w’izuka."
  37,159,"Nihaninahazwe rero Imana Allah mu buryo burengeye cane ivyo ababangikanyamana bayomekera."
  37,160,"Ariko rero, abaja b’Imana Allah bemera koko bakeza n’idini ryayo, ntibavuga ku Mana Allah, kiretse ibiberanye n’icubahiro cayo."
  37,161,"Babangikanyamana! Mu vy’ukuri mwebwe hamwe n’ibigirwamana musenga mu gishingo c’Imana Allah;"
  37,162,"Ntimushoboye guhubisha n’umwe mu biremwa;"
  37,163,"Kiretse uwagenewe kuja mu muriro ku bugarariji bwiwe."
  37,164,"Abamalayika bazovuga bati: “Nta n’umwe muri twebwe, kiretse ko afise ahantu hazwi mw’ijuru adashobora kurenga;"
  37,165,"Mu vy’ukuri twebwe, turatonda mu runani, ku murongo mu gusenga Imana Allah no mu kuyumvira;"
  37,166,"Mu vy’ukuri twebwe, tuninahaza twongera dutazira Imana Allah, mu buryo buri kure cane y’ibitaberanye n'icubahiro cayo”."
  37,167,"Ntumwa y’Imana! Mu vy’ukuri ababangikanyamana, ni ukuri bahora binamura bakavuga imbere y’irungikwa ryawe bati:"
  37,168,"“Ese iyo dushikirwa n’Ibitabu n’Intumwa nk’ivyashikiriye abo hambere yacu;"
  37,169,"Ni ukuri twari kuba abaja b’Imana Allah, bemera koko bakeza n’idini ryayo”."
  37,170,"Igihe bashikirwa rero n’Igibabu ca Qor’ani n’Intumwa Muhamadi (nyakugira amahoro n’impuhwe z’Imana Allah), barabigararije bivuye inyuma. Bitebe bitebuke rero, bazomenya ibihano bibarindiriye mu buzima bw’inyuma yo gupfa."
  37,171,"Ni ukuri ijambo ryacu Twebwe Allah, ryaramaze gushingwa ku baja bacu mu Ntumwa;"
  37,172,"Ko mu vy’ukuri ari bo bategerezwa gutsinda no kunesha abansi babo;"
  37,173,"N’uko ingabo zacu ziduharanira, zitegerezwa kunesha abansi bazo, kuko ari zo zeniherezo ryiza."
  37,174,"Ntumwa y’Imana! Irengagize abatemera ubarabishe amaso, gushika igihe bagenewe kubaho gihere maze bapfe, hanyuma bahanwe;"
  37,175,"Tenyenya rero, uzoheza wirabire ibizobashikira ku kugarariza kwabo, bitebe bitebuke, na bo nyene bazoheza bibonereko ibizobashikira mu bihano!"
  37,176,"Ntumwa y’Imana! Karashize ingani bihutire gusaba ko ibihano vyacu bibashikira!"
  37,177,"Burya, igihe bashikiwe n’ibihano vyacu, hazoba ari igitondo kibi cane ku bagabishijwe hanyuma ntibumva!"
  37,178,"Ntumwa y’Imana! Birengagize ubarabishe amaso rero, gushika igihe bashikiwe n’ibihano vy’Imana Allah;"
  37,179,"Tenyenya rero uzoheza wirabire ibizobashikira ku kugarariza kwabo; bitebe bitebuke, na bo nyene bazokwibonerako ibizobashikira mu bihano!"
  37,180,"Nihaninahazwe rero Imana yawe Rurema Allah, Nyenicubahiro c’iteka mu buryo burengeye cane ivyo ababangikanyamana bayomekera."
  37,181,"Intumwa zose rero zirakagira amahoro, iteka n’itekane bivuye ku Mana Allah."
  37,182,"Nihashimagizwe Imana Allah, Umubungabunzi w’ibiremwa vyose mu buzima bwo kw’isi no mu bw’inyuma yo gupfa."
